%N A396442 Decimal expansion of Sum_{k>=1} (zeta(2*k)/k)*(7/10)^(2*k).
%D A396442 H. M. Srivastava and Junesang Choi, Zeta and q-Zeta Functions and Associated Series and Integrals, Elsevier Insights, 2011, p. 273, eq. (38).
%F A396442 Equals log(7*(sqrt(5)-1)*Pi/10) = log(7*Pi/(5*phi)), where phi is the golden ratio (A001622).
%F A396442 Equals log(Gamma(3/10)*Gamma(17/10)).
%e A396442 0.999990297411009657150261848145682378623593853842994...
